(604,'The Novice Squad Leader learns to manage groups of individuals in combat.  They learn ways of boosting morale, of directing special unified attacks against enemies, and of easing leader-to-group communication.  The Squad Leader\'s abilities are powerful, but only take effect if the Squad Leader is in charge of their group.  By using the /sysgroup command, the Squad Leader can send a system message to their group-mates.'),
