(688,'The Jedi Initiate has just begun the journey down the road of becoming a Jedi. Before becoming a full Padawan Learner, the Initiate must first learn the basics of wielding a lightsaber, using innate healing powers, and exercising control over the Force. The Initiate begins his or her career as a covert member of the Rebel faction.'),
