(690,'The basics of wielding a laser weapon are taught, including safety, maintenance, and some beginning combat moves.'),
(691,'Correct stances can be the key to executing rapid and efficient attacks with a lightsaber. With this, one can string several attacks together to make an effective combination move.'),
(692,'Concentration and self-awareness are of utmost importance when fighting with a lightsaber. Maintaining control while in combat can allow one to strike his or her opponent in a critical location.'),
